title: Annovera birth control vaginal ring effectively prevents unwanted pregnancy, research finds

title_detail.value: Annovera birth control vaginal ring effectively prevents unwanted pregnancy, research finds

summary: A recently approved contraceptive vaginal ring -- the first that can be used for an entire year -- is a highly effective birth control method, according to new clinical trial data.
